ison Finch. Publication date 4 January 2012","feed":null,"feeds":null,"favicon":"http://www.bbc.co.uk/favicon.ico","description":"Robert Hill, Director of the Northern Ireland Space Office, explains how he is inspiring young people from all over the world to see the value and wonder of space.","datetime":"2012-01-04 12:00:00 +0000"}
